Package: ZoopCounter
Type: Package
Title: Zooplankton Counter
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bennett McAfee
Maintainer: Bennett McAfee <bennettjmcafee@gmail.com>
Description: Opens a tally counter designed for counting Zooplankton, but can be used for any tallying purposes. Use ZoopCounter() with a list of names to create a window with the counter. Use and edit keyboard shortcuts to make counting faster.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    gWidgets2,
    gWidgets2tcltk,
    stringr,
    utils
